<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        habt von Nikel Tenners und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> bey
                        ewch <expan>lig<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir wol ver<expan>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu <expan>ewer<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> Hannsen Göldlein,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, mit ew <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                        reden. Und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch, was
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> von der <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
                        sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>, daz ir
                        im das <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawben wellet. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Katherine.</ab>
</div>
